# Day 28 – Hospital Admission Readiness Simulator

## Project Overview
Built a Hospital Admission Readiness Simulator as a single HTML application using Claude AI.

## Features
- Provider & Physician Information
- Diagnosis & Admission Type Selection
- Prior Authorization Status
- Admission Readiness Analysis
- Workflow Actions
- Risk Tracking
- Governance Snapshot
- Final Admission Decision
- Responsive Healthcare UI

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- Tailwind CSS
- Vanilla JavaScript

## Key Learnings
- Built a healthcare workflow simulation.
- Learned admission readiness evaluation concepts.
- Improved frontend development and prompt engineering.
- Designed an interactive healthcare-themed UI.

